Database of representative transcript models for protein-coding genes in 3T3 cells and for the poly(A)-tail length standards.
Transcript models from the UCSC refFlat table for mouse had their 3' ends re-annotated using 3P-Seq (Jan et al., Nature 2011) data from 3T3 cells; only genes detected by 3P-Seq are included in the table.
Coordinates of mouse genes are based on the mm9 genome assembly.
